I"p<p>A simple equation has changed the way that we live. It is having a greater impact than any of the ground breaking theories from science. The reproduction number $R$ is being used to change our behaviours to reduce the spread of the <a href="https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/covid-19-pandemic">Covid-19</a> virus and will leave its mark on us well into the future.</p>
